	   <tr><td colspan=2>Once again like so many have stated, This is a high end game item that most individuals will never see let alone roll on which is an impossiblity in itself. Any guild that is capable is not going to roll on it. They have complex point systems or award systems in play for loot. These systems tend to be based on who puts more into the guilds in raid time and attendance etc. If a warrior had points over a cleric or pally or blah blah blah he could bid for it and win. However There are better items out there for them and most probably have them or are saving up for their *dream* item. <br>&nbsp;<br>Cuedainya<br>65 Archeon of Vis Maior<br>Quellious Server</td></tr>
